  <amendments/>
  <summary>3/14/2001--Introduced.
National Recreation Lakes Act of 2001 - Establishes the National Recreation Lakes Demonstration Program and the Federal Lakes Recreation Leadership Council.Amends the Department of the Interior and Related Agencies Appropriations Act, 1996 to provide for the participation of the Bureau of Reclamation and the Army Corps of Engineers in an existing recreation fee demonstration program.Provides cost-share assistance for reconstruction of a recreation facility operated under an agreement with the State or local agency at a project lake.</summary>
